<lb ed="K" n="0577b07"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pK38p0577b0701" rend="margin-left:1em">丁未歲高麗國大藏都監奉
<lb ed="K" n="0577b08" type="honorific"/><g ref="#CB30072">𠡠</g>雕造</p></cb:div>
